summary: Guys... It was happening. I got my letter to come to the ts7 secret sessions. It came with a package of accessories you could...
body: Guys… It was happening. I got my letter to come to the ts7 secret sessions. It came with a package of accessories you could mix and match and wear while you were there. I was on a bus. I was excitedly mingling with everyone about meeting @taylorswift and getting to hear the new album. We had just pulled up to the airport… New York bound… Then…. I woke up. It was such a realistic dream. It was such a deep sleep. That was one of the saddest I’ve been waking up from a dream. Moral of the story? Don’t watch hours of meet and greet YouTube videos before bed. 😭
